      skos:note "a demo-call prospect's business plan targets SMB — described as a bigger market than devs. The business plan a demo-call prospect takes to prospects needs to reflect the SMB pivot. Prior targeting was developer-first (PLG motion per ADR-002)." ;
      narr:theme "SMB is a larger addressable market than developers; business plan and materials must reflect this pivot" .

