      skos:note "a demo-call prospect's core feedback: the product needs to show how aswritten influences AI behavior. Agents should cite which memories shaped their recommendations. This is the 'value demonstration' problem (task-145). Without visible proof of influence, the sales conversation stalls at 'trust me, it works.'" ;
